Pot of Platinum was started as an outlet for my creative side.  As a Science major, I rarely found a public outlet for the 'artsiness' that I've often felt.  When I was younger, I wore whatever was around.  Whatever my parents would buy me.  Over the years, I've learned that I'm able to exude what I feel inside by garbing myself in pretty things.  I've grown to trust in fashion to teach me to learn more about myself.  To help me grow.  POP will be dedicated to sharing what I have grown to love over the years.  The idea being that it will grow as I grow.  And teach, as I have been taught.

column19: My name is Ged, a thirty something guy living in the beautiful city of London. In addition to personal grooming and care forming an important part of my life, I also am quite passionate about writing, photography and exploring what the world has got to offer. I have a massive soft spot for Japan, her people and their absolutely amazing culture and I hope to visit this beautiful country for the first time very soon! I am quite partial to trawling the websites of my favourite skincare and fashion brands and have been known to hunt out a good bargain or two. Currently an entire section in my bedroom is dedicated to this blog which I like to refer to as The Ged Lab Shrine, where I keep all my products and items to be written about on here. By now you have probably gathered I am always up for a chat so please join The Ged Lab Facebook page where you will not only be able to have a good ol’ chinwag with me but you will also be able to stay up to date with my latest posts and giveaways. If you have more of a tweeting obsession, please feel free to connect with me on Twitter!

Olen Valtteri Sandberg, 19-vuotias Olarin lukiosta valmistunut ylioppilas Espoosta. Bloggaamiseni sai alkunsa keväällä 2012, kun löimme yhdessä parhaan ystäväni kanssa viisaat päämme yhteen ja päätimme puolivuotisen harkinnan tuloksena aloittaa yhteisen blogin pitämisen. Hän jättäyti pois leikistä henkilökohtaisista syistä jo alkutaipaleilla, mutta meikäläiselle blogin pitämisestä oli tullut niin sydäntä lähellä oleva harrastus, että päätin jatkaa sitä omin nokkineni. Blogini kasvu on ollut ilmiömäistä: alle puolessa vuodessa ylitti se reilusti merkittävän tuhannen lukijan rajan, eikä suosiolle näy loppua. En koskaan, edes villeimmissä unelmissani uskonut, että saattaisin saavuttaa näinkin suuren lukijamäärän ja olenkin siitä ikikiitollinen kaikille tulevia blogipostauksia odottaville.

Hello all, Alex here. I've decided to start a new blog. This time around I have a better understanding of the internet and the whole point of blogging in the first place. To do it for yourself. This is exactly what I'm doing. With less then a year left in school it's time to start a new journey in life. The question now is where exactly will life take me? One thing for sure is that I will always have a love for self expression through clothing. So, let me PREACH to you what everyone else on the internet already has. I only hope this leads to inspiring others. 
I decided to embrace the fact that every teacher out there has butchered my last name. They must have known all along. So instead of correcting you and saying "Peacher, Not Preacher" I'll be embracing the fact that PREACHing the ways of fashion may be the only way I survive from a day to day basis.
